    <item>
      <title>Using Stacks to Arrange Views</title>
      <link>https://kyungkoo.github.io/post/using-stacks-to-arrange-views/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 May 2021 00:56:26 +0900</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://kyungkoo.github.io/post/using-stacks-to-arrange-views/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;code&gt;Using Stacks to Arrange Views&lt;/code&gt; 에서는 &lt;code&gt;MeetingView&lt;/code&gt; 화면을 를 만들어 본다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;progressviewhttpsdeveloperapplecomdocumentationswiftuiprogressview-추가하기&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://developer.apple.com/documentation/swiftui/progressview&#34;&gt;ProgressView&lt;/a&gt; 추가하기&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://developer.apple.com/documentation/swiftui/progressview&#34;&gt;ProgressView&lt;/a&gt; 를 추가하는 것 자체는 큰 어려움이 없지만, Xcode12.5 기준으로 &lt;code&gt;ProgressView(value:total)&lt;/code&gt; 선언 시, &lt;code&gt;value&lt;/code&gt; 값이 &lt;code&gt;Int&lt;/code&gt; 이면 canvas 에서 아래와 같은 에러가 발생한다.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;initializer &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;init(value:total:)&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; requires that &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;Int&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; conform to &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;BinaryFloatingPoint&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;

----------------------------------------

